        </div>

        <div class="box-inner">
            <img class="work-logo" src="{{asset "img/logo-nmc.png" }}" alt="Bubblews logo" width="33" height="33">
            <p><strong>Web developer and designer -</strong> At New Media Campaigns, I worked on the front-end and back-end with HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Ruby, Rails, Wordpress, and Hifi for political campaigns, non-profits, and businesses. I also designed websites, primarily for political campaigns. It was a lot of fun.</p>

